    <img shttps://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http://www.concordia.ca/cunews/offices/vpaer/aar/2019/02/06/the-future-is-the-city.htmlon LinkedIn" heighttps://www.concordia.ca/content/dam/common/icons/social-media/twitter-round.pngncordia and its scholars are helping define future urban landscapes%0D%0A%0D%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.concordihttps://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http://www.concordia.ca/cunews/offices/vpaer/aar/2019/02/06/the-future-is-the-city.htmlrc="https://www.chttps://www.concordia.ca/content/dam/common/icons/social-media/linkedin-round.pngs story" title="Email this story" height="40" width="40">
